    "html": "<div class=\"newsitem\">\n          <h1>Computer-Science-Career-Fair-2019</h1>\n          <div class=\"newsdate\">\n            <span class=\"day\"> Monday </span>\n            <span class=\"date\">  5 </span>\n            <span class=\"month\">August</span>\n            <span class=\"year\">2019</span>\n          </div>\n          <p>Don’t forget to diarize the sixth annual Computer Science Career Fair to be held on 5 AUGUST 2019!</p>\n          <!--more-->\n          <p>We receive many enquiries from industry regarding job opportunities for\n            Computer Science students who are to graduate. To facilitate interaction\n            between the potential employers and employees, we host an annual Career Fair.</p>\n        </div>\n",
